435
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:31,310
Splňme im tie sľuby zase.

436
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:41,660
Poďte, jedzte a pite.

437
00:34:45,270 --> 00:34:48,810
Poďte, jedzte a pite.

438
